Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.76,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}朝阳在远处升起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.58,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}与昔日见到的景色相似的街角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:23.50,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我已经遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:26.59,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}因为太赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:32.66,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}意料之外的危机 是神的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:33.51,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.28,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}却不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:38.56,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}脑内一片慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:43.93,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使失去了正在寻找的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:50.41,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那天我们所交换的话语 也能成为坐标
